snippet.textDisplay: A very heartfelt gratitude to Kirtidan Gadhvi for giving traditional Gujarati folk music a much needed revamp and putting it back into the mainstream music scene. And that cute little girl, Tanishka Sanghvi - she has such an angelic voice! That innocence and sweetness in her voice so beautifully captures the emotions of a young girl addressing her father and consoling him that she would always be by his side, always be his princess! <3 This left me teary-eyed!
snippet.textOriginal: A very heartfelt gratitude to Kirtidan Gadhvi for giving traditional Gujarati folk music a much needed revamp and putting it back into the mainstream music scene. And that cute little girl, Tanishka Sanghvi - she has such an angelic voice!
